{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 4,
  "title": "第四章（無源）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "道沖而用之，"
    },
    {
      "text": "或不盈，"
    },
    {
      "text": "淵乎似萬物之宗。"
    },
    {
      "text": "挫其銳，"
    },
    {
      "text": "解其紛，"
    },
    {
      "text": "和其光，"
    },
    {
      "text": "同其塵。"
    },
    {
      "text": "湛兮似若存。"
    },
    {
      "text": "吾不知誰之子，"
    },
    {
      "text": "象帝之先。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "沖，中也。道匿名藏譽，其用在中。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "或，常也。道常謙虛不盈滿。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道淵深不可知，似為萬物之宗祖。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "銳，進也。人欲銳精進取功名，當挫止之，法道不自見也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "紛，結恨也。當念道無為以解釋。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言雖有獨見之明，當知闇昧，不當以擢亂人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "當與眾庶同垢塵，不當自別殊。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言當湛然安靜，故能長存不亡。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "老子言：我不知，道所從生。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道自在天帝之前，此言道乃先天地之生也。至今在者，以能安靜湛然，不勞煩，欲使人修身法道。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
